2011年5月至2012年5月，美鐵在全國歡慶成立四十週年，並將5月7日定位“全國鐵路節”。一本里程碑式的著作《美鐵：一部美國史》也出版發行。四台機車塗以“四十週年紀念塗裝”，並牽引列車在全國巡迴展出，共訪問了45個城市和街道，接待超過8萬5千名來訪者。<ref>{{cite web |last=National Railroad |title=Bulletin Board (40th Anniversary Train Ends U.S.) |url=http://www.amtrak.com/ccurl/779/31/Amtrak-Ink-0612.pdf |work=Amtrak Ink |publisher=National Railroad Passenger Corporation |accessdate=2012-07-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108035801/http://www.amtrak.com/ccurl/779/31/Amtrak-Ink-0612.pdf |archivedate=2012-11-08}}</ref>列車由“創世紀”級機車牽引，含有三節聖塔菲鐵路公司行包車、一節餐車。所有機車均採用美鐵舊式塗裝：156號為1型塗裝，66號為2型塗裝，145號為3型塗裝，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://rrpicturearchives.net/showPicture.aspx?id=2392023 |last=Margherone |title=AMTK 145 |publisher=Rrpicturearchives.net |date=2011-02-02 |accessdate=2011-08-28 |archivedate=2011-09-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110930073640/http://rrpicturearchives.net/showPicture.aspx?id=2392023 |deadurl=no }}</ref> 以及184號為4型塗裝。<ref name="crazytiger94">{{cite journal |year=2010-12/2011-01 |title=America’s Railroad Set to Celebrate 40th Anniversary |journal=Amtrak Ink |publisher=Amtrak |location=Washington, D.C. |url=http://www.amtrak.com/servlet/BlobServer?blobcol=urldata&blobtable=MungoBlobs&blobkey=id&blobwhere=1249220414955&blobheader=application%2Fpdf&blobheadername1=Content-disposition&blobheadervalue1=attachment;filename=Amtrak_AmtrakInk-011411.pdf |accessdate=2011-01-18 |archivedate=2012-06-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120627115319/http://www.amtrak.com/servlet/BlobServer?blobcol=urldata&blobtable=MungoBlobs&blobkey=id&blobwhere=1249220414955&blobheader=application%2Fpdf&blobheadername1=Content-disposition&blobheadervalue1=attachment;filename=Amtrak_AmtrakInk-011411.pdf |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |author=Matt Van Hattem |title=New life for old schemes: For Amtrak's Beech Grove shop painters, it's deja vu all over again |journal=Trains|page=15|volume=71|issue=5 |date=2011-05 }}</ref>

首輛提供免費[[Wi-Fi|Wi-Fi]]的列車為2008年波士頓開往[[波特蘭_(緬因州)|波特蘭]]的“[[東北人號|東北人號]]”。2010年起“[[Acela特快|Acela特快]]”，2011年起“[[瀑布山脈號|瀑布山脈號]]”也提供免費Wi-Fi服務。至2012年8月，東西海岸運營的多輛美鐵列車已有免費無線網絡。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.amtrak.com/journey-with-wi-fi-train-station |accessdate=2012-08-27 |title=Amtrak − Plan − Onboard − Journey with Wi-Fi |archivedate=2012-08-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120828224128/http://www.amtrak.com/journey-with-wi-fi-train-station |deadurl=no }}</ref>

2011年11月，美鐵在“[[東北人號|東北人號]]”首度使用電子車票系統，<ref name=etix>{{cite news |last=Billings |first=Randy |title=Amtrak Downeaster rolls out electronic tickets, improved Wi-Fi |url=http://www.sunjournal.com/news/business/2011/11/11/amtrak-downeaster-rolls-out-electronic-tickets-improved-wi-fi/1113947 |accessdate=2011-11-12 |newspaper=Sun Journal|date=2011-11-11 |archivedate=2013-09-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921053856/http://www.sunjournal.com/news/business/2011/11/11/amtrak-downeaster-rolls-out-electronic-tickets-improved-wi-fi/1113947 |deadurl=no }}</ref>至2012年7月30日，電子車票系統已在全路推廣。據美鐵方面宣稱，使用電子車票系統能“更精確的管理列車運營，了解等車旅客實際情況，方便列車管理。同時電子車票還有助於及早發現列車問題，以便車組在第一時間解決。電子客票同樣能簡化美鐵財務管理...”等等。<ref>{{cite web |last=National Railroad Passenger Corporation |title=eTICKETS NOW ACCEPTED ON EVERY AMTRAK TRAIN |url=http://www.amtrak.com/ccurl/197/699/eTickets-Now-Accepted-on-Every-Amtrak-Trains-ATK-12-069.pdf |work=Amtrak News Release |date=2012-07-30 |publisher=National Railroad Passenger Corporation |accessdate=2012-07-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120804023234/http://www.amtrak.com/ccurl/197/699/eTickets-Now-Accepted-on-Every-Amtrak-Trains-ATK-12-069.pdf |archivedate=2012-08-04 }}</ref>

